creator: Monica Hansen Beachwear
descriptionHtml:
Monica Hansen is pleased to introduce her swimwear and beachwear line Monica Hansen Beachwear. As an international swimwear model Monica has an intimate knowledge of the fashion industry in general and swimwear in particular, having been immersed in the industry for the last 23 years. As a model for many of the top brands, she has first hand knowledge of the best materials and most flattering fits. To this she has added her own sense of style and creativity to produce this brand new, highly fashionable, luxury, designer line, which she launched in early 2016.

The line itself is made in Italy from the finest of Italian materials and is manufactured in one of the top factories for many of the high end designer labels. The suits incorporate custom laser cut designs, handmade crochet, real freshwater pearls and novelty fabrics and prints that Monica herself has created.
